title: Ryka Aoki - Light from Uncommon Stars (1)
authors: 10 Years of Hugo Best Novel Nominees 2014-2023 - 54 Audiobooks jZQ 79GB
description: Shizuka Satomi made a deal with the devil: to escape damnation, she must entice seven other violin prodigies to trade their souls for success. She has already delivered six. When Katrina Nguyen, a young transgender runaway, catches Shizuka's ear with her wild talent, Shizuka can almost feel the curse lifting. She's found her final candidate.
